					<h1>Retain information long term. Forget about forgetting.</h1>
					<p>Research suggests that spreading out study sessions over long periods of time beats cramming when it comes down to remembering information long-term.</p> <p>NoteMinders takes advantage of the spacing effect. Just create a note and give us feedback & we'll send them back to you right when you need to see your note again.</p>
				</div>
