					<h1>Email & Text Reminders</h1>
					<p>Noteminders integrate a spaced repetition algorithm<br> (SuperMemo 2) with email & text so you you don't have to use a dedicated program to take advantage of spaced repetition.</p><p>NoteMinders takes the work out of planning when to study so you can focus on studying, not logistics.</p>
				</div>
			</div>
